{
  "stem": "17526.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 97.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That ID card meant being alive or else not being alive.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So people tried to falsify ID cards and got them by hook or crook.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the main object of [INAUDIBLE] was if you were working in a shop which was organized by the Germans for their own advantages.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they needed people to work so they organized these groups.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And these shops provided them with an ID cards as being useful to work.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Like the fact that we survived together, not just for so long, till the very end was that we, the whole family, had cards and we worked in this shoe factory.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this saved us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was also other shops.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a tailor shop which was famous.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And by the way, the people that run those shops were Germans, but they were not as-- their job was to see that the work is being done properly and that production is being done.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they were not actually treating us badly.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But it's through the employment that we survived to be living together.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Otherwise, every couple of months the Jewish [GERMAN], which is the German word for the Jewish council, was given an order to deliver so many Jews.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now, these-- these Jews, mostly young people, were sent to a work camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "At that time, they were not concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The concentration camps came into existence in '42 or '43 when the Nazis-- the SS took over.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were in charge of them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But before, they were actually done by the German authorities, by the occupation authorities.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "These people were picked up from the street and hauled away by truck to certain points and then they were shipped out to camps.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The camps were hard labor, very meager food.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
